{"tid":2204132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"振華數據監控五千名加拿大人 包括特魯多十一歲女兒","createTime":"2020-09-15T23:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T17:07:06.000Z","uid":292987,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b61ffe28eb08613f0bb9b8305c2c5b664fe7ada2","tid":2204132,"uid":292987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T23:32:47.000Z","msg":"目前被解密的資料庫中發現數千個加拿大人的名字，超過一萬六千個關於加拿大的條目，加拿大的政治、法律、學術、商業、犯罪者等人物的訊息被歸納為三等級，分配為一級的，似乎是有直接影響力的人，例如國會議員、高級公務員、學術研究者，剛當選保守黨黨領的奧圖爾（Erin O&rsquo;Toole）也在其內；分配為二級的通常是當權者的親戚，例如總理特魯多的十一歲女兒和國會議員費凱迪的兒子。等級為三的人則是被定罪者，主要是經濟犯罪人物。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/meiti/lf-09152020123114.html/ampRFA?__twitter_impression=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fmeiti%2Flf-09152020123114.html%2FampRFA%3F__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=db3327ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/meiti/lf-09152020123114.html/ampRFA?__twitter_impression=true</a>"},{"pid":"48c85ce58840a2671cc411c0d0f8b96dba67a5b9","tid":2204132,"uid":292987,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T23:34:59.000Z","msg":"深圳數據庫里的台灣名單都有什麼？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/meiti/cm-09152020113802.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fmeiti%2Fcm-09152020113802.html&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=d5b0d346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/meiti/cm-09152020113802.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主持人：所以不僅政要人士，商界、娛樂界也有人被列入名單內？根據你們分析，大概有哪些類別的人呢？<br />\n<br />\n記者：以我們拿到的兩千多筆的台灣數據來看，粗略分為幾類：第一是高知名度的政治人物，第二外交軍警，第三是科技界或是學界人士，第四是地方首長及民代，第五是有犯罪紀錄人士，或是黑道，第六是傳媒娛樂界人士，最後則是上述有關人士的親人、伴侶等。<br />\n<br />\n ⋯<br />\n<br />\n主持人：為什麼他們會蒐集一些知名人物的親朋好友的網路足跡，這有什麼情報價值？<br />\n<br />\n記者：這是個好問題，很多人可能會想，我發圖點贊，跟國家安全有什麼關係？但像是研究信息戰的沈伯洋就給了一個最近香港的例子，<span class=\"red\">比如中國情報單位，可能透過誰在臉書上跟香港民主運動人士有關的發文互動，去描繪出一個圖像，判斷哪些是可能幫助過香港民主人士的帳戶，再進一步鎖定作攻擊。</span>"},{"pid":"254503fcedb4175b9e87014d12b8a325852d8f62","tid":2204132,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T23:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2c3d5acd320383bd1afb19acc3bec782f627e8","tid":2204132,"uid":204227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T23:36:57.000Z","msg":"twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0df03dfddafc42b8fc48a1e1220d0508088c83d","tid":2204132,"uid":292987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T23:38:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36cbd99aa7975f28580e4c0eabfb33a5e441dab","tid":2204132,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T00:17:35.000Z","msg":"欣宜呢？"},{"pid":"85dd50a30527a30f1a59b3f8f691e65fcbf0a70e","tid":2204132,"uid":167394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T00:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426c638ed68a2bc877f7798f7665aa3e82b9b464","tid":2204132,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T00:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5699a87b62de5c753d469f7c8ad45caf9a15eb5b","tid":2204132,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T00:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a227c3f7b07b6d015604fc9a8dad9e7017c1ae","tid":2204132,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T00:25:09.000Z","msg":"強國：係事主自願提供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f527855673715be1dabb2e2e75b85a63b4ca415","tid":2204132,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T00:32:40.000Z","msg":"呢啲真係大數據人工智能應用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位小心唔好留太多個人資料響網上"},{"pid":"72292f4738603a77d777b0a562e4b6fb2639fc1a","tid":2204132,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T00:33:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"117d4b00bc95ae7c93418e30da714ec4815cd90e","tid":2204132,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T00:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58d539be56e94d50d74a201a869a895b854125c","tid":2204132,"uid":79869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T00:43:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f521365425f67d1d0a997c974681d1a3bc7e39b","tid":2204132,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T17:07:06.000Z","msg":"推推推"}]}